  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group for Sustainable Flood and Drought Management",
  "purpose": "Provides a forum for parliamentarians and interested stakeholders to discuss water level and flood risk management. With a particular interest in catchment management, sustainable drainage and water resource management, better partnership working, and the maintenance of existing flood and drought related assets.",
